Santy is Home is a fun and challenging game where you will help Santy, a cute character, overcome challenges in a house full of obstacles. With this Chrome extension, you can enjoy the game right on your browser without having to install additional software.

In the game, you will help Santy move through rooms, solve puzzles and overcome obstacles to complete missions. Try increasingly difficult levels, and discover many interesting secrets hidden in the house.
